{"tid":343564,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳 業 坤 送 自 己 當 生 日 禮 物","createTime":"2017-08-01T14:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T07:15:37.000Z","uid":35964,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"07dacb72a7b674f980484ec4addd9fd0b661e264","tid":343564,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T14:32:11.000Z","msg":"藝人歐陽震華（Bobby）最近忙於拍攝無綫劇《誇世代》，適逢前日（28日）是他57歲生日，台前幕後為他舉行小型派對慶生，同劇演員龔嘉欣及吳業坤（坤坤）亦有出席，坤坤更帶同結他到場，似乎在派對上獻唱贈興！心情靚爆的Bobby更將黏有蛋糕碎的包裝紙親自餵給坤坤食，他表現受落，更搞笑地留言：「Bobby哥份生日禮物就係我！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20170730/photo/0730-00282-035b2.jpg?t=1501597473360\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170730%2Fphoto%2F0730-00282-035b2.jpg%3Ft%3D1501597473360&h=e1ec1e2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b635cbfe8429f728a404056d534ea10341dd25a","tid":343564,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T14:40:06.000Z","msg":"狗黎？"},{"pid":"527f058aa3378d3d53309c0d9fa215a1a3e5c043","tid":343564,"uid":45931,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T14:59:11.000Z","msg":"坤狗你條廢物渣宰幾撚時死呀<br />\n死坤狗正閪屎"},{"pid":"d04cd40b3c28f63bb3fde82c0ddaad131b57d677","tid":343564,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T15:55:06.000Z","msg":"嘩 佢食呀食 又食得幾過癮喎"},{"pid":"3d4f8a687e3ba1ecd70b1ce0c473d595b5f0b7fa","tid":343564,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T07:15:37.000Z","msg":"收皮啦佢"}]}